window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>For years, they stalked us. Kidnapped us. Dissected us. For years, we feared them. </p><p>Some call them \"gray aliens\". Some claim they crashed in Roswell. Others say they're just a myth. </p><p>But legends often spring from terrifying truths. There are monsters in the dark. And their evil knows no bounds. </p><p>We've faced aliens before. But nothing like this. This enemy is stronger, smarter, and crueler by far. And they want to kill us all. </p><p>But we refuse to fall. </p><p>We will muster all our courage. All our strength. We will tell the enemy: \"Earth will rise!\" </p>"; 
